                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Uhl</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Williams</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-01-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 25, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Apply for permission to examine and copy the record in Sanguily’s case. If
                    granted, have same copied and transmit here.</p>
            </div>
